snippet.title: BATS: Blood Sucker Anti-Terror Squad - Scorpion Supreme Global Domination
snippet.description:
Scorpion Supreme has the world at his command under the threat of his poisonous bite and his STING strike force. The only team that has a chance to stop him is the nocturnal and deadly BATS team.

Based on the coolest animated TV show that never was, BATS stars Count Bloodvayne and the rest of Bloodsucker Anti-Terror Squad as they battle Scorpion Supreme and the ruthless terrorist organization, STING!

Out Soon on:
Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1642110/BATS_Bloodsucker_AntiTerror_Squad/

Xbox One: 
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/bats-bloodsucker-anti-terror-squad/9pb3wg35dgs9?activetab=pivot:overviewtab

Nintendo Switch: Coming Soon

PlayStation 4: Coming Soon
